Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德….
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德….
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在赫夫曼遗迹那里见到艾尔了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的精神还不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是他现在正在艾尔大陆上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我最近得到的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们运气真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到那么大的海啸竟然都没有受什么伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过….
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德和里昂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘船晃得还真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想不想出去走走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜….你也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这片森林…..感觉真诡异耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一路上，似乎都没有看到什么小动物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这片森林完全感觉不到生气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不会又是因为…咒术天球的影响吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…照你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林里的动物难道…全被魔物…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么味道啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是受到咒术天球影响所冒出的毒气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一情况比我以前看到的还要糟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是那些魔物的魂魄的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小长?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼!闻了我就想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小圆?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看这一带…现在已经变成这些魔物的栖息地了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔物的栖息地?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾…..这片大地已经完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你们现在还是尽快离开的好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里已经没有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们搭船去拉库尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个地方….至少比较安全一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真的很感谢各位对我们的关心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们早就已经决定要留在这片土地了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神父
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们从出生就是在这里长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于我们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这片大地就像我们的母亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你们忍心拋下已经生病的母亲离开吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们活到这把年纪从来没离开过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都爱这片土地，也以这片土地为荣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们生长的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的要死的话，也要死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么话啊…..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样太奇怪了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这样是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这并不表示我们放弃希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并不是放弃希望而一心等死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而是我们还一直抱着一丝希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『当这块大地－艾克斯贝尔…\N受到欺凌，民不聊生的时候…』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『便会出现一位异国打扮的勇者』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『勇者高举着光剑，拯救苦难的人民』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的…勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧佩菈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天慢慢凉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能借我看一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这似乎还可以使用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问……这是用来做什么的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得克洛德一路上都非常宝贝它的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪你会不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了和远方的人说话而发明的机器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和远方的人说话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多远呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和宇宙空间通话也许不太可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是在这个行星上的话…应该可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们能用它跟克洛德说话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕没有办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方必须也要有一个相同的机器才能够通话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在有什么打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔大陆太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们现在也只能折回拉库尔大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是你想…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是雪萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪萤火虫?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这附近的人，都把它叫做『大地的精灵』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也认为它们是喜悦和希望的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜悦…..和希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像欧佩菈找寻艾尔尼斯特一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去找克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道艾尔大陆现在非常危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不想逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想离开这个地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见他…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何，我一定要见到他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也许比较好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑟蕾努…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修顿…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啰，我们也要和蕾娜一起去找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…..我们是好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧，小长?小圆?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道还不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还动得了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它一定能再动的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实啊….每次看到你的时候，我都会想…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道是什么东西\N驱使你对每件事…抱持…这种信念?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想要超越一座山…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是一座高耸的大山…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想要超越那座山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别看我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脑袋最不灵光了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受损太严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一般的科学家恐怕得投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你放心，我一定能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德他们有没有事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德他们在那波大海啸来袭之前就上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想他们应该不会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他们在海上遇到了海啸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可就什么都完啰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个悲观主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你也用不着踢我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利亚?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是咒术天球坠落的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的情况怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利亚…过去曾经被喻为艺术之都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是艾尔大陆上最繁荣的一个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是……自从那颗魔石掉下来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切的荣景都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且….现在那个地方已经成了魔物出没的魔域了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:13:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们人类根本就连一步都不敢随便靠近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些魔物都是由咒术天球繁衍出来的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊!我们就在这里吃便当吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都快饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么话啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是才刚刚上路的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在发育饿得快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小长跟小圆呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快，快，快，你给我乖乖的走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子再饿一点吃起便当来，才会更好吃的，阿修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛好痛…瑟蕾努…. 你们救救我啊….
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么啦 蕾娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到克洛德的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里 克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经看不到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我到这边去找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去那边找…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你发出的声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不….. 别过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要….
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…..求求你……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你….救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见面以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他见面之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧?蕾娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德….
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
